Name: How can I search for employers or see who is attending this job fair?
Description: Please refer to job listing page on our website.

Name: How many opportunities can I apply for?
Description: Students are encouraged to apply for at least one opportunity they are genuinely interested in and able to participate in.

Name: What are the requirements needed to apply for a job?
Description: For the requirements (CV, cover letter, etc.), please navigate to the respective recruiter's website.

Name: Where can I apply for jobs?
Description: The job openings will be available on our job listing page, when you want to apply for the position offered, you will be redirected to the company page.
